{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-work-template-js","path":"/quizwars/","result":{"data":{"page":{"id":"06f4b7e1-7b27-5635-985e-b0ac3f2255ab","html":"<p class=\"align-center\">\n<a class=\"btn\" href=\"http://quizwars.herokuapp.com\" target=\"_blank\">Launch demo app</a>\n</p>\n<p>QuizWars is an R&#x26;D experiment that I did while working at SapientNitro. My aim was to learn about realtime bidirectional communication between the server and the clients.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.60000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"1\"\n        src=\"/static/d3056ea9239b9afbdf0cf556e489c570/18e3b/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d3056ea9239b9afbdf0cf556e489c570/d1f95/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/d3056ea9239b9afbdf0cf556e489c570/18e3b/1.jpg 960w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>I also wanted to learn more about Node.js and sockets. I decided to use the Sails.js framework and build a quiz app. You can learn more about the project in the <a href=\"/tutorial-how-to-build-a-multi-player-quiz-app-with-sails-js/\">tutorial article</a> I wrote about it.</p>","fields":{"prefix":"2015"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Quiz Wars","categories":"sapientnitro web prototype ux design sockets sailsjs spa inverted open-source","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/380f2ba550f510d02559995868a17c8d/f3583/logo.png"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/quizwars/","source":"work"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}